{
  "stem": "985.1",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There was a second anti-Semitism-- the fact that my sister was older, as I said, who graduated gymnasium high school who wanted to study-- wanted to go to medical school.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So she couldn't be accepted because of being Jewish.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So she had to go to Vienna University.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then subsequently, when Hitler invaded Austria, then she inscribed into the university in Brussels.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But then the war broke out.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And she never continued.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So in that sense, we did experience anti-Semitism.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Otherwise, on a personal basis, I did not experience.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Did you know what was happening to the Jews in Germany?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I knew when they started coming to Poland en masse after '36, '37, then I learned from the newspapers.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But we were so far away from that, it really-- and I was a young boy.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So I don't know how much really I was involved in it or even interested in that time.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, none whatsoever.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There was no reason, because the fact is that-- well, first I have to mention that when the war broke out in '39, the Germans came in.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They occupied our part for about a week or 10 days.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But then according to their agreement between the Russians and German, they left our part.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And the Russians came in.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And then occupied our territory for two years until 1941.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So there was no reason for us to-- my father was not politically involved in any way, although we had a large house-- in order to be able to stay in this house and maintain it, we had to take three or four families to live with us so we could stay in our house.",
      "word_count": 55
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Otherwise, we supplement my father's ability to through his previous position was retained by the Russians.",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
